### 4 Nova MCP Servera + Refaktoring

---

### Komponenta 1: `mcp-research` (Akademski Istraživački Agent)

#### [NEW] [server.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/.mcp/mcp-research/src/mcp_research/server.py)

**Odgovornost**: Akademsko istraživanje van Kaggle-a — naučni radovi, PubMed, arxiv.

**Alati:**
- `search_papers(query, domain)` — pretražuje arxiv/scholar besplatne API-je
- `get_domain_knowledge(topic)` — čita iz `tactic_registries/` + KB
- `summarize_findings(paper_urls)` — sumarizuje nalaze

**Model**: Groq Llama 3.3 70B (besplatan, 1000 req/day, brz)

**Ugrađeno znanje**: §5 Memory Integrity, §7 Anti-Regression iz GEMINI.md v4.0

---

### Komponenta 2: `mcp-ml-engine` (ML Agent)

#### [NEW] [server.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/.mcp/mcp-ml-engine/src/mcp_ml_engine/server.py)

**Odgovornost**: Feature engineering, model selekcija, hiperparametar tuning, ensemble strategija.

**Alati:**
- `suggest_features(dataset_profile)` — predlaže feature-e na osnovu profila podataka
- `evaluate_model_choice(models, phase)` — provera diversiteta po §3 3-6-2
- `propose_ensemble(model_predictions)` — predlog za blending/stacking
- `check_correlation(pred_a, pred_b)` — korelacija između modela

**Model**: Groq Llama 3.3 70B (primarni) → Google AI Studio Flash (backup)

**Ugrađeno znanje**: §3 Execution Framework, §4 Guardrails, Golden Recipe (Tačka 33)

---

### Komponenta 3: `mcp-kaggle-master` (Kaggle Community Agent)

#### [NEW] [server.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/.mcp/mcp-kaggle-master/src/mcp_kaggle_master/server.py)

**Odgovornost**: Praćenje Kaggle diskusija, komentara, leaderboard-a, notebook-ova.

**Alati:**
