**Model**: OpenRouter Free (Llama 4 Maverick) → Groq Llama 3.3 (backup)

**Ugrađeno znanje**: §6 Tactic Registry, [competition_tracker.md](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/tactic_registries/competition_tracker.md), Anti-patterns (Tačka 31)

---

### Komponenta 4: `mcp-orchestrator` (Supervisor Agent)

#### [NEW] [server.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/.mcp/mcp-orchestrator/src/mcp_orchestrator/server.py)

**Odgovornost**: Centralni supervisor — prima zahtev, konsultuje agente, donosi odluku.

**Alati:**
- `process_request(user_request)` — analizira zahtev i identifikuje relevantne agente
- `consult_agents(agents, question)` — šalje pitanje relevantnim agentima
- `reach_consensus(responses)` — analiza odgovora, konsenzus po §4 Security Invariants
- `get_current_phase()` — vraća fazu (thesis/antithesis/synthesis) iz config-a

**Model**: Google AI Studio Gemini Flash (250 req/day primarni) → Groq (backup)

**Ključna logika — Mandatory Consultation Protocol:**
```
1. Primi zahtev korisnika
2. Klasifikuj: [RESEARCH | ML | KAGGLE | TACTICS | MIXED]
3. Ako MIXED → konsultuj SVE relevantne agente
4. Ako specifičan → konsultuj odgovarajućeg agenta + OBAVEZNO mcp-guardian
5. Sakupi odgovore → primeni consensus (VETO > WARN > PASS)
6. Loguj odluku u GUARD_LOG.md
7. Vrati odgovor korisniku
```

