## Besplatni API Servisi — Mapa

| Servis | Besplatan Limit | Modeli | Koristi ga |
|--------|----------------|--------|-----------|
| **Groq** | 30 RPM, ~1000-14400 req/day | Llama 3.3 70B, Llama 3.1 8B, Mixtral | Research, ML, Guardian |
| **OpenRouter** | 50 req/day (bez kupovine) | 24 besplatna modela (Llama 4, Mistral Small) | Kaggle Master |
| **Google AI Studio** | 250-1000 req/day | Gemini Flash, Gemini Pro | Orchestrator |
| **HuggingFace** | 300 req/hr, $0.10 krediti | Mistral-7B, Zephyr, Falcon | Fallback za sve |
| **Colab** | T4 GPU besplatno | — | Fine-tuning (QLoRA) |
| **Kaggle GPU** | 30h/nedelja | P100/T4 | Fine-tuning + trening ML modela |

